Class AbstractAtomicModelDescriptor

    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.architectures.AbstractAtomicModelDescriptor

    AtomicModelDescriptor

    public abstract class AbstractAtomicModelDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, ModelDescriptorI
    The class AbstractAtomicModelDescriptor implements a descriptor for atomic models to be included in simulation architectures overall descriptions.
